#-Function--color.set
  Function: color.set
      Desc: turn on/off colorized output from msg.* functions.
          : color is turned off if verbose() is also set to off.
  Synopsis: color.set [ON|1 | OFF|0 | auto]
          : curstatus=$(color.set)
          : oldstatus=$(color.set)
          : color.set off
          : # do stuff... #
          : color.set $oldstatus
#-Function--color.set---------------------------------------------------------
